release_note: Object toolbars are now more friendly for your fingers! In a FigJam board tap on an object like a sticky note a shape or text and you ll find refreshed even more touch friendly toolbars ready for you to tap to your heart s content.

The toolbar in FigJam just got a fresh new look and feel! When you re feeling inspired to draw create or jam grab your Apple Pencil and take it for a spin. Other updates include Bug fixes and performance improvements Localization fixes
